	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I see it too: the sidebar moves below the body of the page. I've noticed this on several sites that run MediaWiki 1.15. It doesn't happen on sites running MediaWiki 1.16 or later. If we <a href="http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Manual:Upgrading" class="postlink">upgrade MediaWiki</a>, the problem might go away.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
